location.fullValue: 3-BDRM Country Farmhouse w/Vaulted Master Suite Plan, BUILD ON YOUR OWN LOT (BOYL) OR PROPERTY in VA

data.description: Seller will pay $3,000.00 in buyers closing costs. Super Brick Ranch w/3 Bedrooms, 2 1/2 Baths & approx 2200 sq feet. Huge 4 Car detached garage w/approx 960 sq. ft w/plenty of workshop space .Seller has made the following upgrades to the house: Finished lower level, added a new $16,000. deck, new sliding doors w/blinds, invisible fencing, new well pump, new gas range & refrigerator, fenced back yard & added 2 outdoor water faucets.  2 driveways & conveniently located to Roanoke & Rocky Mount. House has heat pump for heating & cooling on main level & baseboard heat. Baseboard heat on lower level.  There are two extra rooms on the lower level that can be used as bedrooms/office,  Owner is leaving the raised gardens & fire pit in back yard. Selling home & garage as-is. Backyard is fenced in Lower level has a brick area with a hole in the wall that is vented outside for a wood stove.  Seller is selling the house & garage as-is.   Living Room w/wood stove insert (never been used & sold as-is) Back yard is fenced in and there is invisible fencing around the whole yard. Air compressor included & sold as-is.
